{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Ghost Frequency</strong> is a first-person horror game that puts you in the shoes of Mark, a seasoned ghost hunter from the <strong>PIT - Paranormal Investigation Team</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/5.gif?t=1738444898\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Alongside his colleague Emily, Mark investigates the mysterious disappearance of two teammates in an abandoned location haunted by a sinister presence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your mission? Survive the night and uncover the chilling mysteries lurking in the shadows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/6.gif?t=1738444898\" />You\u2019ll get to use key ghost-hunting tools straight from the real-world app <strong>Ghost\u00a0Finder\u00a0Tools</strong>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>EMF Ghost Detector</strong>: Track supernatural activity by detecting electromagnetic frequencies and revealing hidden entities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/7.gif?t=1738444898\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>IR Thermal Camera</strong>: See beyond the visible spectrum with this infrared camera, capturing what the human eye cannot perceive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/2.gif?t=1738444898\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>EVP Digital Recorder</strong>: Capture eerie ghostly voices with this specialized device, tuned to record within the EVP audio spectrum.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/1.gif?t=1738444898\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>PIT - Paranormal Investigation Team</strong> is the Italian ghost hunting team known for their adventures and the creation of the <strong>Ghost Finder Tools</strong> app, the ultimate ghost hunting tool with over a million downloads and used in 170 countries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/PIT.png?t=1738444898\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Do you have what it takes to face the unknown and survive?</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3173740?t=1738444898","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3173740?t=1738444898","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/bb97171ab1508986db5050bb3d0ad25ef36a204e/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738444898","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/bb97171ab1508986db5050bb3d0ad25ef36a204e/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738444898","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[5],"notes":"Includes content that may not be appropriate for all audiences."},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":3272570,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<h1>WISHLIST NOW</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/GHOST_FREQUENCY_wishlist.gif?t=1738444898\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/wishlist.gif?t=1738444898\" /></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Ghost Frequency</strong> is a first-person horror game that puts you in the shoes of Mark, a seasoned ghost hunter from the <strong>PIT - Paranormal Investigation Team</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/5.gif?t=1738444898\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Alongside his colleague Emily, Mark investigates the mysterious disappearance of two teammates in an abandoned location haunted by a sinister presence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your mission? Survive the night and uncover the chilling mysteries lurking in the shadows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/6.gif?t=1738444898\" />You\u2019ll get to use key ghost-hunting tools straight from the real-world app <strong>Ghost\u00a0Finder\u00a0Tools</strong>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>EMF Ghost Detector</strong>: Track supernatural activity by detecting electromagnetic frequencies and revealing hidden entities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/7.gif?t=1738444898\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>IR Thermal Camera</strong>: See beyond the visible spectrum with this infrared camera, capturing what the human eye cannot perceive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/2.gif?t=1738444898\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>EVP Digital Recorder</strong>: Capture eerie ghostly voices with this specialized device, tuned to record within the EVP audio spectrum.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/1.gif?t=1738444898\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>PIT - Paranormal Investigation Team</strong> is the Italian ghost hunting team known for their adventures and the creation of the <strong>Ghost Finder Tools</strong> app, the ultimate ghost hunting tool with over a million downloads and used in 170 countries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/extras/PIT.png?t=1738444898\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Do you have what it takes to face the unknown and survive?</p>","developers":["Serafini Productions"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173740/header.jpg?t=1738444898","is_free":false,"legal_notice":"2024, Serafini Productions \u00a9 All Rights Reserved","linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257062179,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257062179/movie480.mp4?t=1728865871","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257062179/movie_max.mp4?t=1728865871"},"name":"Ghost Frequency - Trailer featuring PIT","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257062179/77258c88706570def063ce40099c0d780336fd3f/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1728865871","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257062179/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1728865871","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257062179/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1728865871"}},{"highlight":false,"id":257061655,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257061655/movie480.mp4?t=1728539122","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257061655/movie_max.mp4?t=1728539122"},"name":"Ghost Frequency - Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257061655/e622dfc14a16508d451fc324f073a11867223983/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1728539122","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257061655/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1728539122","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257061655/movie_max_vp9.webm